{"tid":1997065,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我還是處於認識論","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T09:08:28.000Z","uid":47901,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f938d2dd348152005a13be56fad6574908597d7","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"我還是處於認識論， 無錯，始終我一直受到的教育係&quot;呢個世界係一個鐘擺世界&quot;， 即係世界的一切運作基於物理因果， 所有野可以在物理法則上的因果上追尋根源或預測後果<br />\n<br />\n但係， 我覺得我要脫離呢個&quot;鐘擺世界觀&quot;框框， 因為係呢個世界觀上打轉， 我覺得沒有意義， 我生命不得解脫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算CPU快多一萬倍， 就算造到人造太陽....... 對我的生命有何意義？ 在我呢一生所經過的時間， CPU快了不知多少倍， 能源供應或能源儲存Device好了不知多少倍（例如電池技術同二， 三十年前比可謂天淵之別）， 我地在&quot;鐘擺世界觀&quot;的框框下， 唯有以追求工業技術的進步， 追求財富的積聚， 同名聲地位，同沈溺於電視劇之類所營造出的幻象之中，以此作為&quot;止痛藥&quot; 去減輕&quot;驚懼憂患悲傷寂寞&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但我只見整個社會， 世界， 包括我自己， 在慢慢沈淪， 墮落， 而我信相痴纏在&quot;鐘擺世界觀&quot;， 同當今社會規範（或&quot;吹捧&quot;）的&quot;通用價值觀&quot;， 例如正常人要結婚生子， 人的價值體現在其擁有的資產上等等， 人生不得解脫， 只係作為社會機器中的一個齒輪，磨蝕後要更換丟棄掉， 浪費了上天俾我在此世間的珍貴時間<br />\n<br />\n我都係唔想參與呢個&quot;人世間&quot;的怖慄遊戲， 我覺得其性質有少少似電影&quot;恐懼鬥室&quot;， 只係冇咁血腥， 但要磨好耐好耐<br />\n<br />\n然而當人有獨立思想，但又仍然糾纏在這個&quot;人世間&quot;的怖慄遊戲，其怖慄悲痛會是以十的倍數計，因為你還得作為箭靶去承受萬箭穿心<br />\n<br />\n這是一個迷宮，何日可以走出去?"},{"pid":"d01af975580df4b943d07eb37f4a0d075432144d","tid":1997065,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdab3e222374ec377b2272315e206c92f6eb7c8","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d01af975580df4b943d07eb37f4a0d075432144d","tid":1997065,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6631cbe8e7f24f7395ab42c4f67acc1ad849400e","tid":1997065,"uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇你個標題, 就睇到&quot;我還是處&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以為你想討論&quot;成人禮&quot;問題"},{"pid":"02d3dd8c2ed5c6c4436ccb9af07395d213b2dfa6","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6631cbe8e7f24f7395ab42c4f67acc1ad849400e","tid":1997065,"uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇你個標題, 就睇到&quot;我還是處&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以為你想討論&quot;成人禮&quot;問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b15990872326839ea70f50f683aade036ce0065","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6631cbe8e7f24f7395ab42c4f67acc1ad849400e","tid":1997065,"uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇你個標題, 就睇到&quot;我還是處&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以為你想討論&quot;成人禮&quot;問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"題材又來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28158fede2a28ea05a39734294782f5a08161b5","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"請發大家表意見"},{"pid":"ca70672d1085ebdb7ea123ae2d25bd3cee1f7f3b","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c28158fede2a28ea05a39734294782f5a08161b5","tid":1997065,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"請發大家表意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T14:17:33.000Z","m